17. Already disliked button indication from homepage and pop up
//i[@class='ml-4 far fa-thumbs-down fa-2x liked']

18. Post date 
//div[@class='post-date']

19. Comment field in a pop up 
//input[@placeholder='Comment here']

20. Application version in footer 
//div[contains(text(),'Version: 2020.3.1.4200')]

